info.description:
Text602 was a very popular word processor for IBM PC MS DOS
compatibles, used in Czechoslovakia. T602Parser provides
a simple class modelled after HTMLParser that can be 
used to parse Text602 documents (MS DOS version, not Win602)
and to extract/convert data contained in them.
info.name: t602parser
info.summary: T602Parser - a 602 word processor parser for Python.
